items.description: by copying the calculation into the appropriate column.
however if you do you will need to change the formula in 1st and 2nd hour columns.  Remember the first two hours after 10 are at double time and thereafter triple time.
eg. If a unit assistant does 2 hrs regular o'time on a 10 hour day he will do 3 hours of uncontracted overtime on a 11 hour shooting day resulting in 1 hour of triple time.

Payroll Tax is calculated on the total of fees (incl.Holiday Pay), Overtime and Super.
Workers Compensation is not paid on Super.
